Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}字幕转换助手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.55,0:00:03.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k155}流動的水沒有形狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.69,0:00:05.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k214}漂流的風找不到蹤跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.63,0:00:07.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k194}任何案件的推理都取決於心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.59,0:00:09.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}今天超級跑車一案將有答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.63,0:00:10.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}我從來沒看過這種手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.50,0:00:12.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k87}唯一揭開事情的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.63,0:00:14.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k213}外表看似小孩，頭腦卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}他的名字就叫...名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.85,0:00:21.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k222}正因為你和我是不同的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.99,0:00:30.73,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喜好不同 腳程與表達的方式也大異其趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.46,0:00:37.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如今我們在兩人的記憶中正在漸漸褪色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.43,0:00:45.14,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我摸索過 卻開始探尋其他人與未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.27,0:00:52.28,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我比自己想像的活的更堅強 追尋一種特別的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.41,0:00:56.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}為難以應付的每一天所苦惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.49,0:00:59.56,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}true heart for mystery eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.69,0:01:07.03,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}為了不再迷惑 請別鬆開你的手腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.30,0:01:09.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}即使是互相傷害的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.07,0:01:21.33,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我只是一直在迷惘的時空中找尋答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.68,0:01:27.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}朝著下一個舞台 you take you way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.48,0:01:31.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}請抱緊我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.39,0:01:38.86,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}I feel so all in secret life
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.61,0:01:44.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在商店街抽到一等獎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.53,0:01:46.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}獎品是免費一日游
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.53,0:01:48.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}所以我們就來到伊豆高原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.57,0:01:51.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}那間旅館的老闆是個跑車迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.70,0:01:53.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那天正好是古董車展示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.57,0:01:57.78,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}開幕的前一日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.78,0:02:00.61,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是在埸的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.70,0:02:05.45,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}都說社長騙走了他們的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.57,0:02:09.65,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那晚，社長開車出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.53,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}隔天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.61,0:02:16.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}被發現死在愛車的駕駛座上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.57,0:02:23.32,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}198 超級汽車陷阱(後篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.71,0:02:37.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麼樣，醫生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}死因可能是廢氣瓦斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.75,0:02:41.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}吸入過多二氧化碳中毒而中毒身亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.75,0:02:45.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}除此之外沒有發現其他外傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.92,0:02:47.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}死亡時間推斷為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.71,0:02:49.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}早上九點到十點之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}對了，九點多時後用手機打給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.80,0:02:54.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那時候他還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.71,0:02:56.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}你說什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.75,0:02:57.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}那時候他的情況是怎樣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.63,0:02:59.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k88}聽起來是很痛苦的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.75,0:03:02.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}這裡是哪裡，怎麼一片漆黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.84,0:03:05.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}說一些莫名其妙的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這或許是中毒後的現象吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.88,0:03:12.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是說也在接電話之後去世的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.96,0:03:15.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麼，橫溝警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.88,0:03:18.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}這麼說寺泉社長在九點之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就一直在這裡了，對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.75,0:03:22.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}這還用問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.75,0:03:24.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}還有，毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.75,0:03:26.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}關於駕駛座旁的車窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.80,0:03:29.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}為什麼稍微打開一些呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是生存反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.80,0:03:34.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}因為吸到廢氣而痛苦的寺泉先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.88,0:03:37.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在無意識之下打開的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.88,0:03:40.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}既然這樣為什麼還會死呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.88,0:03:42.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為打開車窗的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.75,0:03:45.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}已經是來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.88,0:03:50.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.71,0:03:52.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}而且還是直線被隔開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.80,0:03:56.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.80,0:03:59.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}不可以在這裡亂動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對不起，我在想這黑色的污跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}到底是什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.92,0:04:06.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是燃料不完全燃燒時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.80,0:04:09.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}所產生的焦油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.92,0:04:12.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然後從排氣管滴下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.92,0:04:15.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這種古董車是常常會發生的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.92,0:04:17.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}呃，外表看起來這麼新穎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.84,0:04:20.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}是啊，上面差不多找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一個指紋的的乾淨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.84,0:04:26.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}怎麼，發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.80,0:04:28.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}這輛車子最近好像撞過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.80,0:04:31.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}左邊車燈罩上有裂痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.96,0:04:33.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}並且附著了衣服纖維之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.80,0:04:38.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}裂痕和衣服纖維
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.84,0:04:42.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k213}讓大家久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.84,0:04:47.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}首先請第一發現者的相良先生..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.71,0:04:49.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.88,0:04:52.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k217}請你說明一下發現的情景好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.96,0:04:55.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大約是早上十點多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.92,0:04:56.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}駕車回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.75,0:04:59.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k83}正要把車子停回停車埸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.92,0:05:02.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}差點撞上迪諾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為霧還沒有散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.96,0:05:07.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}後來我往迪諾的駕駛座看過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.88,0:05:09.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}發現寺泉無力的攤在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.88,0:05:12.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}有沒有發現其他不對竟的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那時候其他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.88,0:05:19.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}都聚集在進入停車埸之前的路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.09,0:05:20.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對不起，那都是因為我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}什麼，蘭小姐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.88,0:05:25.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}因為小蘭突然大叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.00,0:05:28.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大家嚇了一跳，結果都跑過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為在大霧中，警備員突然叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.96,0:05:33.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}害我嚇了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.88,0:05:34.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.80,0:05:37.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k92}關於去世的寺泉先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在駕車回來之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.88,0:05:42.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}一直開著引擎留在車上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.00,0:05:47.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}由於廢氣過量而引起中毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.13,0:05:51.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}為何開著引擎留在車上?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.13,0:05:52.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}各位有沒有什麼意見?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.88,0:05:54.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}其實社長對那輛車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.92,0:05:56.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}就像自己的小孩一樣疼愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.88,0:05:58.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}就連昨天也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.92,0:06:01.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}社長，其他的車子已經放好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.05,0:06:03.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}社長的車子也可以準備做展示了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.92,0:06:06.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}等等，不用那麼急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今晚我想和它單獨在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為開始展示以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.96,0:06:16.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}就不能像平常一樣想開就開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以我想，社長回來之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.92,0:06:22.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}暫時不想離開愛車吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.17,0:06:23.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原來如此，所以很自然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.92,0:06:27.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}就留在車上睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}社長對於這次的展示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.92,0:06:32.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}不知道期待了多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一想到這，實在太遺憾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.96,0:06:37.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}別再耍猴戲了，經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.05,0:06:37.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.84,0:06:38.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k79}其實社長死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}你倒鬆了一口氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}你說這是什麼話!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.96,0:06:43.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}我可是知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.84,0:06:47.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k88}你曾被社長捉過把柄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.09,0:06:50.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}把柄?是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.09,0:06:51.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他...他說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.00,0:06:56.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}但是我並沒有恨過社長啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.17,0:06:57.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不像他們幾個，呃!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.00,0:07:01.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}"不像他們幾個"是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.09,0:07:05.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大家都很恨那個社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.21,0:07:06.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大家都因為拿愛車做抵押
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.96,0:07:08.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}向寺泉先生借錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}而且還有恐嚇信，叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}恐...恐嚇信!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.96,0:07:16.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}那只是一個惡作劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.09,0:07:19.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.13,0:07:22.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不過這樣一來，也有可能是謀殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.09,0:07:23.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}謀殺?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}要怎樣利用廢氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}讓對方中毒身亡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.00,0:07:28.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}但是，毛利先生...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.88,0:07:30.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k88}橫溝警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.00,0:07:32.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}最重要的是證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.05,0:07:34.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}叔叔不是常常這樣說的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.00,0:07:36.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}柯南，你說的對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}各位，如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.05,0:07:42.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}那位偵探先生打電話的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}寺泉不是還活著嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.05,0:07:48.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}在那之後，我們一直和他在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}嗯，那時候不在一起的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.05,0:07:54.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}相良先生還有那位勝呂先生二個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.25,0:07:56.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我也算嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.05,0:07:59.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}討厭，我沒和大家在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.13,0:08:01.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是為了準備開幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}大約是十點到十點五分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.00,0:08:06.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}才五分鐘而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}之後聽到蘭小姐的尖叫聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.05,0:08:11.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}馬上跑到停車埸來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.21,0:08:14.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}只有五分，怎麼讓人中毒身亡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.13,0:08:16.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}你這樣說也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.09,0:08:20.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}相良先生，你說你去游車河了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.05,0:08:25.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}回想起來，發現社長屍體的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.05,0:08:27.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}也是相良先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.05,0:08:27.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.96,0:08:31.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k91}相良先生，難道真的是你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.17,0:08:33.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不是，不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.05,0:08:35.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}昨天我聽到相良先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.09,0:08:37.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}在房間與某人講話的內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.05,0:08:41.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}放心，包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.30,0:08:44.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}明天下午三點就會開幕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.21,0:08:47.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k291}所以今晚是最後的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.21,0:08:50.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對，不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.21,0:08:52.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}總之按照計劃進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.09,0:08:55.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}知道了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.21,0:08:59.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}相良先生，到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.05,0:09:04.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其實我是去找朋友借錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.34,0:09:04.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}借錢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.00,0:09:07.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k66}對，我想把錢還給寺泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.09,0:09:10.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k209}然後拿回車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.21,0:09:12.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是就這樣還給他，太無趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.09,0:09:14.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}所以就想在展示的當天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.13,0:09:17.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}當埸還給他，讓他下不了台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.21,0:09:21.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以昨晚飛車到東京去借錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.09,0:09:24.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你可以打電話給我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.09,0:09:26.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}他可以替我作證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.13,0:09:30.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}看來全部的人都有不在埸證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.05,0:09:35.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這一定是意外死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.34,0:09:38.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對不起，警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.21,0:09:40.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}為了去世的社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.17,0:09:43.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}我想將迪諾放到展示埸去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.25,0:09:47.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這樣啊，現埸檢驗也結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.34,0:09:48.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.00,0:09:50.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k66}謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.13,0:09:52.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k213}如果不是相良先生的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.13,0:09:53.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}那到底是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.05,0:09:57.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k92}咦，那個人昨晚...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.00,0:10:00.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.13,0:10:02.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k213}嗯，什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.13,0:10:04.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}剛才檢查的哥哥說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.17,0:10:07.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}迪諾的車頭燈罩上有裂痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}呃，真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}昨晚還沒有發現呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}而且如果是社長撞到的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.17,0:10:17.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}一定會馬上找人修理，且大吵一番
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}果然是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.21,0:10:23.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}寺泉先生是駕車回來之後撞到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.09,0:10:27.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是，犯人是用什麼手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.30,0:10:29.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}殺害寺泉先生的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.17,0:10:31.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.17,0:10:33.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}你不會聽錯吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.21,0:10:35.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}是的，我來到停車埸是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.17,0:10:37.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}正好十點之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.21,0:10:40.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}社長的車子並沒有在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.30,0:10:42.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是會不會因為霧太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.17,0:10:43.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}所以忽略了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.13,0:10:47.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k96}不，我不會弄錯社長的車子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.42,0:10:49.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為那裡停了別的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.17,0:10:51.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}別...別的車子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.21,0:10:54.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}對，因為有霧，所以看不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.34,0:10:57.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好像是藍色的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且那引擎聲音我從未聽過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.25,0:11:02.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}應該不是旅館的常客才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.34,0:11:05.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麼那輛車子的引擎是啟動的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.34,0:11:07.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對，如果是社長的車子引擎聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.21,0:11:09.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}我一聽就會知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.21,0:11:11.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}到底是怎麼一回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.25,0:11:15.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}橫溝警官，請過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.46,0:11:16.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.13,0:11:18.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k67}對了，野田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.21,0:11:20.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}那時候是不是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.25,0:11:22.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}什麼，你說相良先生他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.25,0:11:24.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}對，他說錢已經還清
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.25,0:11:28.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}所以想馬上把車子拿走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.46,0:11:30.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的，在這麼忙的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.21,0:11:33.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}我們走  是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.38,0:11:36.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小朋友，你為什麼會知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}果然是那樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.25,0:11:41.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}嗯，和你說的一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.38,0:11:44.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這樣我終於明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.38,0:11:46.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}焦油直線被隔開的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.30,0:11:50.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}停車埸那輛藍色車子的真正身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.50,0:11:55.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還有車頭燈罩的裂痕和纖維物體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.21,0:11:58.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}一切的謎已經解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.38,0:12:03.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯人就是...那個人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.30,0:12:08.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}別這樣，相良先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.38,0:12:11.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這樣我很難做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.30,0:12:13.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}錢的話，我剛剛已經還清了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.25,0:12:15.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}總之我要把它給開回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.30,0:12:17.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}等一下，相良先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.30,0:12:21.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}各位，怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你來的正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}相良先生想把賓士給開走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.30,0:12:26.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}我們怎麼勸都不聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.17,0:12:28.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k87}這是不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.34,0:12:30.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k217}總之在這件事情告一段落之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.30,0:12:31.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}絕對不能離開這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.21,0:12:33.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k91}你說事件...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.34,0:12:35.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k213}這不是普通的意外事件嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.30,0:12:38.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}事情好像沒那麼簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}發現什麼線索了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.34,0:12:43.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}其實是野田警備員正好在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.42,0:12:46.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}十點之前到停車埸巡邏的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.42,0:12:48.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看到的不是寺泉先生的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.34,0:12:51.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}而是一輛藍色的車子停在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.46,0:12:54.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什麼!這麼說的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.42,0:12:56.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k296}來了  來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.34,0:12:57.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}叔叔，你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.21,0:12:59.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k87}毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.34,0:13:03.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k213}我終於明白了，橫溝警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}聽到你剛才說的話之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.34,0:13:07.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}我已經全部解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}你的意思是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.38,0:13:12.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}寺泉先生並不是意外死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.46,0:13:17.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是有計劃性的殺人案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.42,0:13:24.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}橫溝警官，在解開謎底之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.59,0:13:26.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我想請你幫我準備一些東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.38,0:13:29.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}知道了，你要我準備些什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.50,0:13:32.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}首先可以找野田警備員過來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.50,0:13:35.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂，去叫    是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.50,0:13:38.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還有就是一個大的塑膠袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.50,0:13:43.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果可以的話，像車罩之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.34,0:13:46.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}車罩啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}對了，勝呂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.42,0:13:50.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}平時都是你負責替停車埸的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.42,0:13:53.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}套上車罩的吧?   是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.50,0:13:57.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的嗎，可以借給我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.63,0:14:02.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}嗯，可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.30,0:14:10.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}既然已經準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麼我們就開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.38,0:14:15.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}犯人用藥將回到停車埸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}寺泉先生昏睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.38,0:14:20.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}讓他坐在迪諾的駕駛座上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然後發動引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.42,0:14:26.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}那麼我是不可能進行殺人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為我要開車去東京的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.42,0:14:33.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}寺泉的車子還沒有回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.30,0:14:35.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那可不一定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.42,0:14:37.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.42,0:14:41.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}因為沒有人見到寺泉回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.67,0:14:43.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麼如何證明在你離開之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.42,0:14:46.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}寺泉還沒有回來呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.55,0:14:48.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.42,0:14:50.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}別吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.42,0:14:51.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}但是，毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.34,0:14:55.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k92}野田警備員在發現屍體之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.71,0:15:00.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}說在停車埸並沒有看到寺泉的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.42,0:15:03.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其實車子就在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.59,0:15:06.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}野田警備員在巡邏停車埸的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.59,0:15:09.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是那裡只有一輛藍色的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.59,0:15:14.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那輛車子就是寺泉先生的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.38,0:15:16.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什...什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.50,0:15:19.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}但是野田先生說引擎聲不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.59,0:15:24.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的，那並不是社長迪諾的車聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.42,0:15:27.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是別的車子的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麼，橫溝警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.46,0:15:32.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}你試著將迪諾的引擎發動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.59,0:15:37.34,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.59,0:15:44.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利先生，引擎發動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.63,0:15:48.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好的，野田先生，你覺得呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.71,0:15:50.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}果然不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.50,0:15:53.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}不是在停車埸的引擎聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麼，橫溝警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.55,0:15:59.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}你試著將車罩蓋在迪諾上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.75,0:16:03.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}呃...這個車罩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.71,0:16:05.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.55,0:16:07.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}野田先生，準備好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.50,0:16:09.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}你仔細的聽聽看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.46,0:16:14.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k196}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.42,0:16:23.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是這個 是這個聲音，警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.55,0:16:28.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}但是為何要替迪諾蓋上車罩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊!原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}所以才會拉下車窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.59,0:16:36.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}正是，所以車窗才會拉下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.75,0:16:41.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}為了讓廢氣灌入車內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.50,0:16:44.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯人讓寺泉先生睡著之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.67,0:16:46.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}將迪諾的車窗稍微拉下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.55,0:16:52.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}用車罩將車子給蓋住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.67,0:16:56.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}讓車罩緊貼著地面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大家是否還記得?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.55,0:17:00.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}寺泉先生在電話中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.55,0:17:02.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}最後的一句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.55,0:17:06.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.80,0:17:09.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂，社長嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.67,0:17:11.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}是我，毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.59,0:17:14.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}你現在在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.71,0:17:16.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這...這裡是在什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}怎麼一片漆黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.59,0:17:21.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}一片漆黑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.71,0:17:27.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原來如此，社長說一片漆黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.59,0:17:30.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}正是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.71,0:17:35.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然後廢氣沿著車罩流動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.59,0:17:38.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}從打開的車窗進入車內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.63,0:17:41.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}進而讓車內的寺泉先生中毒死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.75,0:17:46.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然後找機會將車罩拿走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.59,0:17:50.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這樣完全犯罪就成立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.84,0:17:52.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.63,0:17:55.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}發生了犯人意想不到的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.80,0:17:58.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是什麼?什麼意想不到的事情?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.75,0:18:00.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k295}第一就是被野田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.67,0:18:03.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}看到車子被蓋上車罩的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.71,0:18:04.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.55,0:18:06.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k84}野田先生說在那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.67,0:18:09.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}其實並不是要到停車埸去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.75,0:18:12.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的，是經理要我去停車埸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.75,0:18:15.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看看社長的車子回來了沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.75,0:18:18.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然後另一個就是小蘭的尖叫聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.75,0:18:20.59,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}呃，我的叫聲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.67,0:18:25.38,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}對，我想犯人正在取下車罩時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.59,0:18:29.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}聽到小蘭的叫聲而驚慌起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.88,0:18:32.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}結果忘記把車窗給關起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.80,0:18:35.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}就是說，那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.80,0:18:40.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}最後跑到小蘭那裡的人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.59,0:18:51.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}勝呂先生，就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.59,0:18:56.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}勝...勝呂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.92,0:18:59.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.63,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k288}因為聽到小蘭小姐的叫聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.67,0:19:02.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}我是最慢來到的一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.63,0:19:04.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k96}因此就說我是犯人的這種事情..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.71,0:19:07.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k208}勝呂先生，你褲子上的污跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.80,0:19:12.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.67,0:19:15.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是你昨晚不小心用紅酒撒到...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.84,0:19:17.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}的確是，不過在那之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.71,0:19:21.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}你送酒店招待來我們房間的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.96,0:19:24.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對了，剛才弄髒了你的褲子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k284}真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.71,0:19:28.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k191}沒關係，沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}我馬上換掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.75,0:19:34.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}既然這樣你為何又換上髒褲子呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.96,0:19:36.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是我的自由啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.71,0:19:40.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k175}寺泉先生的車燈罩上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.00,0:19:44.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有個裂痕，裡面還有纖維物質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.00,0:19:48.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你為了讓剛回來的寺泉先生停車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.96,0:19:50.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不小心撞到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.75,0:19:54.92,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k179}結果將的褲子給扯破了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.96,0:19:57.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這種事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k292}這全是你捏造出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.75,0:20:01.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k187}野田先生，你在停車埸發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.75,0:20:03.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}陌生的車子之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.80,0:20:06.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}為什麼不過去調查呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.88,0:20:08.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那是因為在那裡的勝呂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.80,0:20:10.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}要我去檢查一下旅館的照明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.71,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}你亂說!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.80,0:20:15.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}勝呂先生拿來的車罩後面部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.88,0:20:18.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你們將它掀起來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.88,0:20:22.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那裡應該有黑色液體附著在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.00,0:20:26.96,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}應該有一段時間了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.96,0:20:28.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}的確有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.80,0:20:30.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k184}上面有毛利先生所說的黑色污跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.75,0:20:32.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k195}在發現屍體的現埸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.75,0:20:34.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}從迪諾的排氣管流出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.80,0:20:37.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k205}焦油的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.92,0:20:40.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}好像是被什麼給擋住一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.92,0:20:43.84,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}留下一條直線的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.92,0:20:45.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果仔細調查的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}可以發現兩輛車的焦油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}都是同一種成份的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.80,0:20:50.67,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}好何，勝呂先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.71,0:20:55.42,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k91}這樣你還要說自己是清白的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.71,0:20:59.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啍，對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.92,0:21:01.75,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是我殺了寺泉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.84,0:21:06.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k192}那輛迪諾...原本是我的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.05,0:21:10.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是那個寺泉將它給騙走的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.09,0:21:12.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就因為這點小事，你就殺了他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.96,0:21:14.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k287}你說只是為了這點小事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.84,0:21:19.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}別把我和那些有錢人混為一談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.05,0:21:21.88,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}拿到即將被廢除的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.96,0:21:23.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k291}每天不吃不喝的一點一滴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.84,0:21:25.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k188}慢慢的讓它變得那麼光滑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.84,0:21:30.55,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}而寺泉卻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.42,0:21:49.17,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不知道　該用什麼話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.34,0:21:55.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}才能告訴你我真正的感覺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.34,0:22:06.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}從那時起　不知過了多少季節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.42,0:22:12.21,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}雖然時間無情地流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.34,0:22:18.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你卻總是　微笑地陪著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.34,0:22:29.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我沒對你說出口的  至今還有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.46,0:22:34.46,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Secret of my heart 請你不要懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.55,0:22:39.25,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}無論何時　只要還有少許未來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.42,0:22:45.13,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真相　是緊握在手中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.34,0:22:52.09,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}I can't say 請給我點時間  I'm waiting for a chance
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.97,0:23:02.93,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}去的時候是很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.01,0:23:06.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k204}但是回家卻覺得怎麼這麼累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.10,0:23:10.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這就是所謂去時了了走時怕怕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.22,0:23:14.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}果然還是火鍋自助餐比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.22,0:23:20.18,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸，我們應該讓橫溝警官送我們一程啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.18,0:23:21.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.01,0:23:26.72,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k183}那個傢伙，叫我們一聲也好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.05,0:23:31.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}橫溝警官，你感冒了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.05,0:23:35.05,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}不，剛才突然覺得打起冷顫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.10,0:23:35.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}要小心比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.89,0:23:37.97,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k79}嗯，我從來沒感冒過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.01,0:23:41.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k212}真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.14,0:23:45.89,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我絕對不會再幫你了!
